                        "content": "Ahhh yes, this is the time of year to take a look back, before taking a look forward. I like to dive into AirlineReporter's analytics and see what stories were the most popular and where you readers are from. Some of you maybe thinking &quot;well heck David, there haven't been as many stories this year.&quot; Well, you would be right. I do not want to make any sort of grand statement that we will soon be back to the days of having a daily new story... but I hope we find a happy place in the middle. And for those who love to see our new stories, but aren't sure when they post, make sure to sign up for our newsletter and we will send you an email when we publish a new story (sweet self plug, right?).\nLet's take a look at the most read stories, what cities and countries our readers are from, and some other nerdy odds and ends!",
